Name: Aisling and the Tavern of Elves
About the game: “Aisling and the Tavern of Elves” is an Isekai Fantasy-Comedy Dating Sim Visual Novel, where you play as Aisling Whitehorse, a hapless mercenary turned tavern owner eking out a living in the Elven Kingdom of Eiredagh. - A charming and hilarious storyline in a High Fantasy setting. - Beautiful anime-style character art - Orchestral and folk music soundtrack - Multiple endings
